# Report a Problem



<img src="https://images.code.org/a858e7fc8aa0e391359c7059bbcad2f1-image-1714074767673.46.57 PM.png" alt="The Code.org 'Contact Us' submission form." style="float: right; width: 400px; clear: both; margin: 0 20px 20px 20px;">

#### 1.  While logged in click the   ?   menu
#### 2. Select "Report a problem".
#### 3. Describe the issue in detail, including screenshots and links when possible
#### 4. Submit your message, and our team will follow up via email to assist you.


### **What Happens Next?**

#### After you submit your message, a member of our team will follow up with you via email. 

